  "description": "This individual presents as an animated corpse of indeterminate age, with pallid light skin drawn tight over sharp cheekbones and a recessed jawline. Dull gray eyes sit beneath heavy, darkened sockets, fixed in an unblinking stare characteristic of cavern-dead revenants. Thin white hair persists in a loose, uneven fall, clinging in wisps along the scalp and nape. The frame is lean and desiccated, with bony hands and rigid posture that emphasize the body’s unnatural preservation.",
